{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"60e0c095b7","title":"进行教育革命要依靠无产阶级革命派","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"00694dfd49","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":25,"articleId":"60e0c095b7"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"7ab1c4ae34","name":"教育革命","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4875363bf3","type":"paragraph","text":"关于按系统实理革命的大联合的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"6918c501f1","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年十月十七日）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"2e0825dd22","type":"paragraph","text":"各工厂、各学校、各部门、各企业单位，都必须在革命原即下，按照系统，按照行业，按照班级，实现革命的大联合，以利于促进革命三结合的建立，以利于大批判和各单位斗、批、改的进行，以利于抓革命、促生产、促工作、促战备。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"2e00f52b6d","type":"paragraph","text":"（转引自1967年10月18日《人民日报》）对海重学习毛主席著作积极分子代表","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"b4ef8dd45a","type":"paragraph","text":"大会代表的","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"fd29594f34","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年十一月十九日）","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"b9c6bf59e8","type":"paragraph","text":"这个象章好（指海军学习毛主席著作积极分子代表大会敬献给毛主席的象章一—编者），有海军又有空军，又有这么多群众，我就放心了。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"1e3e5003e0","type":"paragraph","text":"进行教育革命要依靠无产阶极革命派","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"b45688b4bf","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年十月二十五日）","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"1f946e758b","type":"paragraph","text":"进行无产阶级教育革命，要依靠学校中广大革命的学生，革命的教员，革命的工人，要依靠他们中间的积极分子，即决心把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底的无产阶级革命派。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"3d093d3268","type":"paragraph","text":"（转引自1967年10月27日《人民日报》在发表《关于教育革","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"adb80e9812","type":"paragraph","text":"命的几个初步方案》时所加的“编者按”。）对《解放重报》1967年11月9日社面","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"d981d11fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"《抓好形势教育》的重要修改","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"e2333a574c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年十一月）","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"a627ac52e8","type":"paragraph","text":"在社论的第三段，毛主席特地重新引用了1938年10月他在中国共产党六届六中全会上的报告中的如下两段话：“当前的运动的特点是什么？它有什么规律性？如何指导这个运动？这些都是实际的问题。”“运动在发展中，又有新的东西在前头，新东西是层出不旁的。研究这个运动的全面及其发展，是我们要时刻注意的大课题。","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"0520d0a1a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（见《中国共产党在民族战争中的地位》，《毛泽东选集》","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"5952e9c05f","type":"paragraph","text":"第二卷第二版523页）","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"60e0c095b7"},{"id":"79a3f26764","type":"paragraph","text":"341","inde